<title>USA: USA Detergents names new president/COO.</title>
<headline>USA Detergents names new president/COO.</headline>
<dateline>NORTH BRUNSWICK, N.J. 1997-07-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>USA Detergents Inc said Wednesday it has named Giulio Perillo as its new president and chief operating officer.</p>
<p>Effective August 4, Perillo will succeed acting President Uri Evan, who remains chairman and chief executive.</p>
<p>Most recently, Perillo was vice president and general manager of Centeon Bio-Services Inc, a subsidiary of Centeon LLC.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
